# Path to the folder that contains the solution category folders
# (OJI, ONI, Baraj + Lot ..., etc.).
#
# In production the website lives in a /website subfolder of the solutions repo,
# so the default ".." already works and you can leave this unset.
#
# For local development, point it at a local clone of the solutions repo:
# SOLUTIONS_DIR=C:/path/to/Romanian-Olympiad-Solutions
SOLUTIONS_DIR=
